original: Milton, Axel Johan Tage, bankdirektör, Sölvesborg, f. 16/5/09 i Ramkvilla, Jönköp. !l. Anst. i Skand. Bankens tjänst sed. 31, kon t xhef o. verk-st. dir. v. bankens- kont. i Sölveisborg sed. 45.
translated: Milton, Axel Johan Tage, bank director, Sölvesborg, b. 16/5/09 in Ramkvilla, Jönköping. Employed in Skand.
